## Create paid vacation with intersecting dates

* Login
* Click Vacations button
* Click create vacation button
* Set vacation dates "12 Aug 2019" "15 Sep 2019"
* Click Create in form
* Click Vacations button
* Click create vacation button
* Set vacation dates "10 Sep 2019" "18 Sep 2019"
* Click Create in form
* Check backend errors and close them
* Click close vacation form

## Open created vacation and change it

* Login
* Click Vacations button
* Open created vacation
* Change vacation Day From "9 Aug 2019"


